<p>and thanks for the observations - I&#39;ll try to upload version 1.1. in the coming weeks as I&#39;ve gotten some good hints about how to improve the &#39;playability&#39; of the PDF in general. </p>

<p>Regarding the mechanics,in my mind some of the ones you mention are not mechanics but tactics (bluffing) or strategies (diplomacy) which can be achieved by executing particular mechanics, such as different communication mechanics. But this is a topic I discuss in my thesis, and there is no space nor need to go into it here. Dexterity for instance is certainly a good one to add.<br />
